OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1775765175
OL,3,CMan accused of attacking former
OL,4,Cpartner's house
OL,6,FA man in Londonderry allegedly turned
OL,7,Fup at the house of his former partner
OL,8,Fof more than 20 years and their three
OL,9,Fchildren with an axe and knife, before
OL,10,Fdriving his car repeatedly into the
OL,11,Fproperty causing significant damage.
OL,13,FEoin Nolan, of no fixed abode, faces
OL,14,F12 charges from the incident that
OL,15,Fallegedly occurred on Tuesday 7 April.
OL,16,FThey include four counts of
OL,17,Fthreatening and abusive behaviour, and
OL,18,Fthreats to kill.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
