OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1775765175
OL,3,CMan accused of attacking former
OL,4,Cpartner's house
OL,6,FAt Londonderry Magistrates' Court on
OL,7,FThursday, a police officer said Nolan
OL,8,Farrived at the property in Altcar Park
OL,9,Fwith a clear intent of causing harm.
OL,11,FThe 36-year-old allegedly attacked the
OL,12,Fhouse - causing considerable damage to
OL,13,Fthe front door.
OL,15,FIt's claimed he then repeatedly drove
OL,16,Fhis car at the property - which has
OL,17,Fnow been left structurally unsafe.
OL,19,FThe court heard that he made threats
OL,20,Fto the police and his former partner
OL,21,Fthroughout the attack.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
