PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1775765175
OL,3,CMan accused of attacking former
OL,4,Cpartner's house
OL,6,FNolan's solicitor said the defendant
OL,7,Fwas hoping the police would kill him.
OL,9,FHe also said the defendant had mental
OL,10,Fhealth issues and that he had recently
OL,11,Fspent some time at a facility in the
OL,12,FRepublic.
OL,14,FHe was denied bail and has been
OL,15,Fremanded in custody.
OL,17,FHe'll next appear on 30th April.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/4
